CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1946, pg. 32 reads: "Collecting Star Dust - An enthusiastic fan, Dazzarina Daniels of 54 Bartlett Street, gets signature from delectable Dolores Parker, who is the female vocal feature of the Hines aggregation."
TitMainTitle: Dolores Parker wearing dark strapless dress with sequined detail, seated on bentwood chair, signing autograph for Dazzarina Daniels wearing suit with grid patterned front, in Syria Mosque for Night of Stars
